   <text>
      <body>
         <div>
            <pb facs="1865_02_09_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Kreglinger_Co_Amsterdam_1.tif" n="envelope"/>
            <p>
               <seg rend="center">
                  <watermark style="textOrientation: upside-down">
                     <orgName type="firm" ref="K01036">KREGLINGER &amp; CO</orgName>
                     <lb/>
                     <placeName ref="K00529">AMSTERDAM</placeName>
                  </watermark>
                  <lb/>
                  <hi rend="latintype">
                     <hi rend="underline">via <placeName ref="K00515">Marseille</placeName>
                     </hi>
                     <lb/> De Heeren</hi>
                  <stamp type="postal" style="rectangular">FRANCO</stamp>
                  <stamp type="postal" style="round">
                     <placeName ref="K00529">AMSTERDAM</placeName>
                     <lb/>
                     <date when="1865-02-09">9/2</date>
                     <lb/>18-5<lb/>65</stamp>
                  <stamp type="postal" style="round">
                     <placeName ref="K00549">PAYS-BAS</placeName>
                     <lb/>
                     <date when="1865-02-11">11<lb/>FEVR.<lb/>65</date>
                     <lb/>VALNES</stamp>
                  <hi rend="latintype">
                     <orgName type="firm" ref="K01004">L. Kniffler + Co.</orgName>
                     <lb/>
                  </hi>
                  <stamp type="commercial" style="oval">
                     <orgName type="firm" ref="K01036">KREGLINGER &amp; CO.</orgName>
                     <lb/>AMSTERDAM</stamp>
                  <lb/>
                  <hi rend="latintype">
                     <hi rend="underline">
                        <placeName ref="K00502">Japan</placeName>. <placeName ref="K00514">Nagasaki</placeName>
                     </hi>
                  </hi>
               </seg>
               <lb/>
               <add style="writingMode: vertical-lr; textOrientation: sideways-right" place="marginRight" resp="other">1865<lb/>
                  <placeName ref="K00529">Amsterdam</placeName>
                  <date when="1865-02-09">9/2</date>
                  <lb/>
                  <orgName type="firm" ref="K01036">Kreglinger + C</orgName>
               </add>
            </p>
            <pb facs="1865_02_09_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Kreglinger_Co_Amsterdam_2.tif" n="2"/>
            <p>Herren <orgName type="firm" ref="K01004">L. <hi rend="latintype">Kniffler + C<hi rend="superscript">o.</hi>
                  </hi>
               </orgName>
               <lb/>
               <seg rend="center">
                  <hi rend="latintype">
                     <placeName ref="K00514">Nagasaki</placeName> - <placeName ref="K00502">Japan</placeName>
                  </hi>
               </seg>
               <lb/> Gegen unser erg. letztes vom <date when="1865-01-06">6 <choice>
                     <abbr>v. m.</abbr>
                     <expan>vorigen Monats</expan>
                  </choice>
               </date> erhielten<lb/> wir Ihre beiden geehrten Zuschriften vom <date when="1864-11-24">24 <hi rend="latintype">Novbr.</hi>
                  <lb/>
               </date> + <date when="1864-12-09">9 <hi rend="latintype">Decbr.</hi>
               </date> Wir entfalten aus Ersterer<lb/>
               <table>
                  <row>
                     <cell>
                        <term type="commercial" ref="K01522">£</term>
                        <measure type="currency" quantity="200" unit="britPound">200.-.-</measure>
                        <lb/>
                     </cell>
                     <cell rows="2">
                        <lb/>6 <unclear reason="eccentric_ductus">m. s.</unclear> auf die
                                    <hi rend="latintype">
                           <orgName type="firm" ref="K01029">London joint Stock
                                        Bank</orgName>
                        </hi>
                     </cell>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <cell>
                        <choice>
                           <abbr>"</abbr>
                           <expan>
                              <term type="commercial" ref="K01522">£</term>
                           </expan>
                        </choice>
                        <measure type="currency" quantity="100" unit="britPound">100.-.-</measure>
                     </cell>
                     <cell/>
                  </row>
               </table> welche prompt <hi rend="latintype">accept</hi> fanden und die wir
                    Ihnen<lb/> unter üblichem Vorbehalt gutschreiben à <term type="measure" ref="K01512">f</term>.<measure type="currency" quantity="11.35" unit="gulden">11.35</measure> mit<lb/>
               <add resp="other" style="transformRotateZ(-45deg)" place="marginLeft">not</add>
               <term type="measure" ref="K01512">f</term>
               <measure type="currency" quantity="3406" unit="gulden">3406.-</measure>
               <hi rend="latintype">p<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                  <date when="1865-02-09">Heute</date>.</hi>
               <lb/> Aus letzterem ersehen wir wohlgehend daß Sie<lb/> den Ihnen durch uns
                    eingeräumten <hi rend="latintype">Credit</hi> auf<lb/> Ihre Firma in <hi rend="latintype">
                  <placeName ref="K00525">Yokohama</placeName>
               </hi> übertragen haben,<lb/> und bereiten wir deren eventuellen <term type="commercial" ref="K01534">Tratte</term>n besten<lb/> Schutz.<lb/> Unser
                    Markt bietet für dortige Artikel<lb/> anhaltend wenig Interesse. Wir nehmen
                    höflich<lb/> bezug an den gedruckten Marktbericht unter<lb/> Kreuzband und
                    zeichnen hochachtend<lb/>
               <seg rend="right">
                  <hi rend="latintype">
                     <orgName type="firm" ref="K01036">Kreglinger + Co.</orgName>
                  </hi>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <pb facs="1865_02_09_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Kreglinger_Co_Amsterdam_3.tif" n="3"/>
            <pb facs="1865_02_09_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Kreglinger_Co_Amsterdam_4.tif" n="4"/>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
   <text type="translation">
      <body>
         <pb facs="1865_02_09_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Kreglinger_Co_Amsterdam_1.tif" n="envelope"/>
         <p>KREGLINGER &amp; CO<lb/>AMSTERDAM<lb/>via Marseille<lb/>De Heeren
                <lb/>FRANCO<lb/>AMSTERDAM<lb/>9/2<lb/>18-5<lb/>65
                PAYS-BAS<lb/>11<lb/>FEVR.<lb/>65<lb/>VALNES <lb/>L. Kniffler + Co.<lb/>KREGLINGER
                &amp; CO.<lb/>AMSTERDAM<lb/>Japan. Nagasaki<lb/>⟨1865<lb/>Amsterdam
                9/2<lb/>Kreglinger + C⟩</p>
         <pb facs="1865_02_09_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Kreglinger_Co_Amsterdam_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <p>Messrs. L. Kniffler + Co.<lb/>Nagasaki - Japan<lb/>Following our respectful last
                letter from 6th of last month we<lb/>received your two esteemed letters from 24th
                Nov. + 9th Dec.<lb/>We found enclosed in the former <lb/>
            <table>
               <row>
                  <cell> £ 200.-.-</cell>
                  <cell>
                     <lb/>6 month view to the London joint Stock Bank</cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell>" 100.-.-</cell>
                  <cell/>
               </row>
            </table> which were promptly accepted and for which we<lb/>credit you under the
                usual conditions at f.11.35 with<lb/>⟨not⟩ f 3,406.- per today.<lb/>From the latter
                letter we see benevolently <lb/>that you have transferred the credit granted <lb/>to
                you by us to your company in Yokohama,<lb/>and we provide best protection for its
                potential <lb/>bills of exchange. <lb/>Our market continues to offer little interest
                <lb/>in articles from there. We refer politely <lb/>to the printed market report
                attached with<lb/>a wrapper and sign<lb/> Yours faithfully<lb/>Kreglinger + Co.</p>
         <pb facs="1865_02_09_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Kreglinger_Co_Amsterdam_3.tif" n="3"/>
         <pb facs="1865_02_09_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_Kreglinger_Co_Amsterdam_4.tif" n="4"/>
      </body>
   </text>
